Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.00,0:00:15.00,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2电影字幕制作【杨雪辉】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.49,0:02:11.72,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2015年  建立月球永久殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.17,0:02:16.90,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2032年  商业开发火星矿产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.61,0:02:24.11,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2040年  发射地平线号太空船 去探索太阳系的极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.69,0:02:30.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但其飞越海王星后  消失于无形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.80,0:02:36.14,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为有史以来最严重的太空灾难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.51,0:02:43.81,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2047年  现在 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.25,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,琪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.85,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想念你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.66,0:05:40.25,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(白日太空站  近地球轨迹) 威尔博士  请登上洛斯克号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.12,0:05:53.13,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美国太空指挥总署太空船: 洛斯克号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.15,0:05:57.76,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,功能: 搜索救援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.02,0:06:00.40,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离子驾驶 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.44,0:06:06.07,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方向: 矢径1-9度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.91,0:06:14.08,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,航线定好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.79,0:06:20.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离谱到极
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.38,0:06:25.30,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,苦等了半个月  却碰到这差事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.51,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么不去火星? 彼德丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.59,0:06:32.01,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 火星有女人嘛 - 说得对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.76,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海王星什么都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.85,0:06:36.10,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们会孤立无援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位都知道规矩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.98,0:06:42.02,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里出事 我们去哪里 好了 出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.52,0:06:44.23,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 航线怎样?  - 制定妥当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.32,0:06:47.36,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 屏幕讯号没问题 - 贾斯汀先生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.49,0:06:50.07,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我的屏幕上都是绿色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.15,0:06:51.32,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始倒数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.41,0:06:54.49,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离子推进器10分钟后发动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.28,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你  大副
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.37,0:06:57.54,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.62,0:07:00.46,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 史密夫  跟我来 - 是 大副
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.54,0:07:03.58,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 贾斯汀先生  准备引力缸 - 好的 船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.51,0:07:09.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 库珀先生 - 船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.30,0:07:12.63,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 10分钟后发动 - 是时候冬眠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.72,0:07:15.30,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 船长 - 彼德丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.06,0:07:18.18,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒船长  我想 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.39,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士  我们要赶时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.19,0:07:24.48,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史密夫  要三催四请吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.56,0:07:26.23,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 不是的  - 船长 我不想 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.32,0:07:29.11,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请跟大家去引力缸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.19,0:07:30.44,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修妥那个箱子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.53,0:07:34.24,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则要走路去海王星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.32,0:07:35.62,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还要干什么? 彼德丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.70,0:07:38.62,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有些二氧化碳清除器未搬上船  船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.79,0:07:40.66,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你站在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.50,0:07:44.75,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你  DJ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.08,0:07:46.50,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 先脱帽 - 先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.59,0:07:49.25,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 初次躺引力缸? - 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.13,0:07:54.47,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船长不喜欢我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.76,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 别管他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.49,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不习惯有陌生乘客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,DJ呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.35,0:08:01.22,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- DJ - 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.73,0:08:04.81,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.81,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必须要注射吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.90,0:08:10.82,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离子推进器一发动 引力有30个G那么大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.57,0:08:15.16,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有保护 你的骨头就会被压成水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.49,0:08:19.08,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我见过老鼠受引力作用的后果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.87,0:08:24.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畏惧局促?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十分畏惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.72,0:08:36.74,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洛斯克号  出航后56日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.15,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.99,0:09:37.95,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很孤独
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.87,0:09:42.12,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.96,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在这里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.85,0:10:03.85,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.88,0:10:39.01,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.22,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.44,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,琪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.07,0:10:58.03,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在等着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.08,0:11:13.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧 呼吸 DJ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.34,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 威尔博士 不要紧 - 我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.42,0:11:17.67,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 放松 - 我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.42,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.26,0:11:24.68,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢来  你冬眠了56日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.76,0:11:27.47,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,精神会有些恍惚  明白吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.56,0:11:33.27,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我没事  谢谢 - 拿着 不用急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.11,0:11:38.78,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觉得怎样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.78,0:11:42.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 要咖啡吗?  - 什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.32,0:11:45.99,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要咖啡吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.16,0:11:49.49,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要了  谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.00,0:11:52.50,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧 随便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你呢? 斯塔克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.13,0:11:56.96,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要吮吸些又热又黑的东西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.50,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 有兴趣吗?  - 没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.63,0:12:02.76,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 那么 要咖啡吗? - 斯塔克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.84,0:12:05.05,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 船长 - 怎么不到指挥室?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.39,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,介意我先穿衣服吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.47,0:12:09.22,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老实说 介意 我先穿衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.73,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家快点 有正事办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.18,0:12:15.73,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丹尼  他会走  生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.81,0:12:18.02,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈咪  骑牛牛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.48,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,室内不准玩球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.49,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是唯一能追不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.61,0:12:27.49,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 对不起 妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.08,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 好的 - 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.16,0:12:31.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 彼德丝 - 是的  船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.62,0:12:33.91,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我试过找别人代替你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.75,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但匆忙间找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.83,0:12:38.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.34,0:12:42.26,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟前夫商量好 丹尼跟他过圣诞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.34,0:12:45.47,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我过暑假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.22,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.47,0:12:48.85,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿什
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.18,0:12:51.06,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先生女士们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.14,0:12:52.93,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有2小时23分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.02,0:12:56.06,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就抵达海王星上空  非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.15,0:12:58.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 谢谢你 - 非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.48,0:13:01.27,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,操作全部正常  顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.90,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 向总署汇报了没有?  - 汇报了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.99,0:13:05.74,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 各位听着 - DJ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.82,0:13:07.91,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都知道 本船有位客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.99,0:13:10.33,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威尔博士 麻烦你来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.99,0:13:14.50,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来介绍  大副斯塔克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.58,0:13:16.25,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀先生  机房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.37,0:13:18.00,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太空怪客库珀先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.08,0:13:20.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自我介绍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.38,0:13:23.05,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听着 我是你最好的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.51,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,专门救人身 伤人心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.59,0:13:27.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是救援技师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.55,0:13:31.60,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,医疗彼德丝  驾驶史密夫先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.06,0:13:35.23,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在一角的苦瓜干叫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.31,0:13:37.64,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,DJ 创伤处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.40,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.48,0:13:44.61,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,介绍完毕  我有个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.74,0:13:46.65,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么老远跑到这里来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.74,0:13:50.24,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许博士愿意赐教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.57,0:13:51.95,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.83,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先  我很欣慰有机会和你们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.91,0:13:57.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你当然欣慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.29,0:14:00.67,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但要知道我们并不欣慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.75,0:14:02.54,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取消假期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.63,0:14:04.17,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来到这海王星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.26,0:14:07.76,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近的哨站离这里30亿公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.18,0:14:11.68,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次在这样遥远的太空 救和被救的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.76,0:14:17.02,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都同归于尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.02,0:14:21.81,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以下我们说的话  是极度机密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.94,0:14:24.11,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总署接到一个电讯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.19,0:14:26.94,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发自海王星的上空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.99,0:14:31.61,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经查证  电讯来自 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.70,0:14:33.62,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地平线号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.95,0:14:38.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呵 吹牛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.12,0:14:41.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取消假期 为了这个 非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.38,0:14:43.17,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿什  坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.67,0:14:47.01,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,库珀  你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.38,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听他说下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.47,0:14:51.38,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们曾经对外公布 地平线号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在探索外太空时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.97,0:14:58.06,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为反应炉负荷过度所以炸毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.14,0:14:59.73,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实并非如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.81,0:15:03.23,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地平线号是政府秘制的太空船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.31,0:15:06.82,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的是要飞得超过光速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.99,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恕我插嘴 那不可能 根据相对论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.07,0:15:13.82,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有东西快过光速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.49,0:15:18.08,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对  我们不可以违背相对论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.50,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但可以避重就轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.87,0:15:22.58,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那艘船不能快过光速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.67,0:15:25.67,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但能够打开一条时空通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.84,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够刹那间  在宇宙中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.92,0:15:30.34,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从一处到好多光年之外的另一处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.42,0:15:31.67,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.09,0:15:35.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 要用复杂的数学才能解释 - 不妨一试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.35,0:15:39.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简单来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.39,0:15:42.60,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们采用挡磁场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.69,0:15:46.94,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将一小束引力子集中起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.02,0:15:49.11,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后  按照维尔氏张力学把时空折叠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.19,0:15:51.95,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到时空曲率变成无限大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.03,0:15:54.53,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从而产生一个奇点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.62,0:15:56.37,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说通俗点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.45,0:15:59.41,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他妈的  说通俗点 你能不能使用人懂的语言?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.58,0:16:06.54,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假设这张纸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.63,0:16:10.05,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是云尼莎的海报  是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.13,0:16:12.92,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这幅美女代表时空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.05,0:16:19.18,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要从这一点A到那一点B去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.26,0:16:22.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两点之间最短的距离是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.43,0:16:23.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连一条线段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.65,0:16:25.73,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.81,0:16:28.77,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两点之间最短的距离为零
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.98,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时空通道的作用就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.24,0:16:34.49,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将空间折叠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.57,0:16:39.33,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使A点和B点同时同地出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.29,0:16:44.37,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地平线号穿过通道后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.46,0:16:46.50,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空间回复正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.25,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这过程叫引力推进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.80,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 你怎么知道得这样清楚? - 船是我制造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难怪派你来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.51,0:16:59.22,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船既然没有炸毁  发生了什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.30,0:17:03.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起初  航程顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.43,0:17:05.94,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分毫不差 用一般推进器驾驶到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.90,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安全距离外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.98,0:17:09.94,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后获准发动引力推进器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.02,0:17:12.69,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打开到近纪时间区的通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.28,0:17:16.15,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着  船就消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.36,0:17:20.07,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无踪无影  直到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.16,0:17:23.16,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七年来  船到过哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.70,0:17:26.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们来 正为了寻找答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.37,0:17:29.63,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不知道有没有活人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.63,0:17:34.34,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但罗斯福站却接到这电讯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.56,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 究竟是什么鬼? - 听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.64,0:17:51.15,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休斯敦总部把电讯过虑了好几次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.23,0:17:55.36,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到一把似乎是人的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.37,0:18:05.79,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道是不是语言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.91,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 拉丁 - 什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.50,0:18:11.17,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是说 似乎像拉丁语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.25,0:18:14.00,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 你能够翻译吗? - 再播一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.13,0:18:20.68,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在这里 听到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.56,0:18:27.93,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎是"释吾"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.02,0:18:29.06,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他的我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.14,0:18:30.90,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"释吾"?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.69,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.90,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家回到岗位去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.50,0:18:55.71,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驶向水平线  最佳角度14度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.80,0:18:59.30,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 方向3-3-4 - 方向3-3-4
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.38,0:19:02.14,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,航线矢向调到负1-4度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.22,0:19:03.39,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1-4度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.10,0:19:10.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经瞄准了地平线号的导航台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.10,0:19:12.69,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那船在电离层顶部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.77,0:19:15.94,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们似乎 遇到强烈气流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.65,0:19:22.61,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向前慢驶 史密斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.70,0:19:26.53,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 船的情况怎么样?  - 支撑得住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.83,0:19:28.74,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备调整速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.83,0:19:33.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三  二  一  开动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.09,0:19:40.26,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 距离?  - 一万米  逐渐接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.42,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 斯塔克  试试通话 - 好的  船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.51,0:19:43.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到按喇叭 看是否有人听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.51,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是太空总署的洛斯克号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.60,0:19:49.60,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地平线号  你们听到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.68,0:19:50.98,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威尔博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.44,0:19:55.61,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 过来看看 - 那船在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.65,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地平线号  正面五千米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.73,0:20:00.86,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 斯塔克 有没有回应?  - 地平线号 你们听到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.94,0:20:02.99,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三千米  接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.66,0:20:08.74,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么也见不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.50,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一千五百米  太接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.58,0:20:14.71,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 在哪里? - 警戒讯号已经亮起  在前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.79,0:20:17.38,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 一千米 太接近  - 小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.46,0:20:21.13,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,九百 八百 七百
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.22,0:20:23.76,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我们在它上面 - 会撞船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.84,0:20:26.64,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 斯塔克 - 就在那里 老天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.60,0:20:30.64,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒推  全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.90,0:20:45.40,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.01,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.89,0:21:10.22,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好壮观的船 威尔博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.97,0:21:14.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 过奖 - 史密夫  准备同步飞行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.06,0:21:16.77,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乐意之极
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.45,0:21:34.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那主要气门锁上了 我们可以停泊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.12,0:21:35.96,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的 史密夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.04,0:21:39.54,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用机械臂将我们接上那板架去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.97,0:21:50.76,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心  那处不是用来负重的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.51,0:21:54.60,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.44,0:22:00.69,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 一切顺利?  - 接上了地平线号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.77,0:22:02.90,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢 如果有香烟  你可以抽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.98,0:22:05.23,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.40,0:22:09.57,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 斯塔克 有没有发现? - 反应炉仍然热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.66,0:22:11.87,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有小量辐射泄露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.95,0:22:13.99,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但可能并不严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.08,0:22:15.58,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 船内有没有气压?  - 有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.66,0:22:20.42,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船身完好 但里面没有引力 暖气系统停顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.50,0:22:22.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船内极度寒冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.29,0:22:24.59,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船员除非冬眠了 否则不能生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.67,0:22:26.96,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 探测船员 - 已经开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.05,0:22:28.72,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生物探测器开启
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.01,0:22:33.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,探测不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.43,0:22:36.56,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 辐射的干扰? - 不会  辐射不够多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.64,0:22:40.52,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些生命迹象 但浮游不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.60,0:22:43.48,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎遍布全船  怪事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.57,0:22:46.98,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么  我们逐层搜  逐房搜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.07,0:22:48.69,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斯塔克 放出连接带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.78,0:22:50.65,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿什 开动戒备系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.74,0:22:52.49,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.57,0:22:54.70,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀  准备太空漫步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.79,0:22:56.16,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的 船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.25,0:23:02.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士 你坐镇指挥室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.29,0:23:03.63,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.79,0:23:06.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一场来到 不是替你指挥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.30,0:23:08.55,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我必须上那船去 - 我们先确定情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.63,0:23:10.55,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 才接你过去 - 不 对不起 不能接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.63,0:23:13.18,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我必须上那船去 - 我们先确定情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.26,0:23:14.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情就是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.51,0:23:16.31,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要你从这里教我们怎样走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.39,0:23:19.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帮我们完成任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.99,0:23:35.78,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你忘记带工具箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.17,0:23:48.59,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.84,0:23:54.14,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 那些需要修理 - 我会修理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.85,0:23:58.93,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熊宝宝 保重身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.36,0:24:08.02,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,DJ  开工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.49,0:24:12.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,视像清晰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.53,0:24:16.12,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 听到吗? 威尔博士 - 听到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.87,0:24:18.62,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们沿着连接带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.70,0:24:21.62,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接近地平线号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.83,0:24:26.33,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们在气锁门外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.96,0:24:29.50,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开动磁靴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.34,0:24:37.05,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有气压
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.66,0:24:58.70,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船内冰冻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.99,0:25:03.41,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到处是冰的结晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.75,0:25:07.00,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们现在在走廊上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.08,0:25:11.34,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主廊连接船头的工作间和船尾的机房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.59,0:25:16.26,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 贾斯汀先生 你检查机房 - 好的 船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.38,0:25:19.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彼德丝和我检查船头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:29.27,0:25:31.27,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士 这些是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.23,0:25:35.69,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里也有 到处都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.78,0:25:36.86,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紧急情况用来炸毁走廊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:36.95,0:25:40.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把船一分为二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.62,0:25:44.62,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船员用船头作为逃生船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:50.25,0:25:53.88,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在医疗室 没有伤亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.93,0:26:00.14,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,医疗室似乎从来没有用过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.22,0:26:01.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仍然没有看见船员踪迹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.97,0:26:04.77,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果见到 早已告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.98,0:26:08.14,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,探测生命迹象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.44,0:26:13.48,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阴森得像坟墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:16.65,0:26:18.11,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他奶奶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.99,0:26:20.99,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒 你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:21.41,0:26:23.74,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船长神经过敏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.83,0:26:25.91,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,库珀 回去你的工作岗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:26.16,0:26:28.41,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒 你心跳得很厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:28.50,0:26:30.00,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:36.51,0:26:40.09,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威尔博士  我到达第一个船舱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:40.26,0:26:42.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机房就在另一边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:42.51,0:26:44.64,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的 我们进去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:01.99,0:27:05.12,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这究竟是什么地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:05.20,0:27:10.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是用来防止干扰磁场的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.71,0:27:14.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活像个碎肉机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:18.34,0:27:20.05,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在指挥室内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:27.85,0:27:30.06,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里有血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:43.74,0:27:48.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷却剂漏了出来 到处都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:49.95,0:27:53.79,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漏了许多 但仍然安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:05.43,0:28:08.14,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彼德丝 请你转过去 后左
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:09.93,0:28:12.73,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 什么东西? - 航行日志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:32.41,0:28:33.96,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:35.92,0:28:38.75,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡得相当紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:47.01,0:28:49.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么他没有眼睛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:49.51,0:28:53.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 因为急剧降压 - 降压不会造成那情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.02,0:28:58.98,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎受了动物之类的袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:59.11,0:29:02.61,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,软组织有大量擦伤痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:03.15,0:29:04.86,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,僵尸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:07.28,0:29:09.53,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在探测生命迹象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:14.62,0:29:18.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,测到很奇怪的读数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:30.18,0:29:33.02,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我试试加强照明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:43.90,0:29:45.86,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是引力推进器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:52.08,0:29:54.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是船的核心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:09.89,0:30:13.22,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀 我们看不到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:24.03,0:30:25.73,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀 答话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:37.29,0:30:38.50,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 什么事?  - 不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:38.58,0:30:40.50,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生命探测读数急升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:51.64,0:30:53.97,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情况不妙 叫他立刻撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:59.98,0:31:01.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,噢 该死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:05.78,0:31:06.86,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:06.94,0:31:09.11,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 去吧 库珀 - 我们去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:47.86,0:31:50.15,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搜索队 声音中断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:50.57,0:31:53.24,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是米勒 有人听见吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:59.58,0:32:02.71,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 什么回事? - 紧急失压
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:02.83,0:32:06.08,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右舷保护护板毁掉 船身破裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.05,0:32:09.80,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我尽量塞着  你们走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:09.88,0:32:11.92,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气压下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:13.51,0:32:16.30,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气锁有气压衣 去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:16.39,0:32:18.14,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀 我来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:22.52,0:32:24.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熊宝宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:24.69,0:32:26.73,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我快到了 快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:31.53,0:32:33.40,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抓到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:34.24,0:32:36.11,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当心 当心...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:37.41,0:32:40.24,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抓到你了 怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:40.87,0:32:42.12,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稳住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:44.87,0:32:47.88,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒船长 听到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:48.21,0:32:51.96,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 史密夫  你终于开金口 - 情况严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:52.05,0:32:55.47,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右舷隔板毁坏  船身破裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:55.64,0:32:58.26,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安全路线失灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:58.39,0:33:00.18,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 赶得及接好吗?  - 赶不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:00.26,0:33:04.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空气只剩下218公升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:04.44,0:33:06.98,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氧气缸破裂  报废
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:07.06,0:33:10.32,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我们死定了 - 地平线号呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:10.82,0:33:12.07,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:12.15,0:33:14.99,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 有空气 动力 - 我们唯一机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:15.07,0:33:17.20,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那艘船邪门得很
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:17.28,0:33:18.99,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:19.08,0:33:20.91,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总好过坐以待毙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:21.29,0:33:25.08,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有船员登上地平线号  立即
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:25.58,0:33:28.17,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 在气缸集合 - 我先去开启暖气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:28.25,0:33:31.13,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心  引力将恢复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:31.25,0:33:36.51,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引力5秒后恢复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:51.61,0:33:54.82,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀 我要你 睁开眼睛 振作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:18.97,0:34:20.34,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威尔博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:21.89,0:34:23.18,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:23.77,0:34:26.14,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经开动大部分基本系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:26.85,0:34:28.10,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 暂时已经开动 - 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:28.19,0:34:31.98,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我们的情况怎样? - 天线全部中断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:32.07,0:34:35.28,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟外界的通讯完全切断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:35.36,0:34:37.19,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会有救兵到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:37.74,0:34:40.28,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 空气很难闻 - 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:40.36,0:34:42.66,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二氧化碳会随着我们的呼吸而增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:42.74,0:34:45.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地平线号的二氧化碳清除器坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:45.37,0:34:46.91,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把洛斯克号的带去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:47.00,0:34:50.00,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么  空气可以支持20小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:50.08,0:34:52.25,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后  我们最好赶回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:08.60,0:35:12.27,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在左舷  接近吸热器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:16.32,0:35:17.69,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:23.78,0:35:26.24,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒船长 米勒船长  听到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:26.33,0:35:28.70,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到  我们的船怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:28.79,0:35:31.67,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船外壳有一条7米裂缝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:31.75,0:35:35.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以修理  但是需要时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:35.13,0:35:37.71,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽快  空气只够20小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:37.80,0:35:39.13,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:41.76,0:35:43.59,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里出了什么事? 威尔博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:55.06,0:35:57.48,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎样了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:58.07,0:36:02.11,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎活着  但是不省人事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:02.78,0:36:04.03,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很难说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:08.62,0:36:10.58,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能15分钟之后醒来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:12.58,0:36:14.42,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能永远不醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:15.21,0:36:17.25,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道不合常理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:17.34,0:36:21.80,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但贾斯汀突然出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:21.88,0:36:26.51,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核心一时是液体  一时变成固体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:26.60,0:36:28.26,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,物理上不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:28.35,0:36:31.27,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威尔博士  物理你个屁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:31.35,0:36:33.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我亲眼看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:33.44,0:36:35.94,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除非通道打开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:36.02,0:36:39.82,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 对 通道的确打开了 - 引力推进器没有发动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:39.90,0:36:42.32,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎打开?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:42.40,0:36:44.20,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是照实直说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:44.28,0:36:48.62,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 推进器不能自己发动 - 你说话过火了 库珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:49.74,0:36:52.91,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀先生可能死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:53.00,0:36:56.37,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他所遇到的  我们也会遇到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:56.46,0:37:01.17,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,库珀先生自称见过某些东西 我相信他见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:02.05,0:37:04.30,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我需要个解释
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:07.85,0:37:12.02,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恕我老实说句  我认为库珀先生眼花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:12.10,0:37:15.44,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许他见到的是引力歪曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:15.52,0:37:17.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所产生的视觉效应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:17.44,0:37:19.52,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,视觉效应? 他妈的风凉话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:19.61,0:37:21.48,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 风凉话... - 库珀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:21.57,0:37:23.69,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行  我住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:25.82,0:37:28.95,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引力歪曲  怎样发生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:29.03,0:37:33.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果核心漏出一阵的引力浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:34.58,0:37:38.46,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这引力浪会造成时空歪曲 令贾斯汀似乎消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:38.54,0:37:42.00,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也会损坏洛斯克号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:43.01,0:37:47.63,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 但我认为完全没有可能 - 核心内有什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:48.72,0:37:49.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相当复杂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:49.97,0:37:52.72,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多久可以解释清楚? 我们有 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:52.81,0:37:55.31,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,17小时48分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:56.56,0:37:58.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核心内有什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:00.31,0:38:02.82,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:02.90,0:38:05.78,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那三个磁环排列好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:05.86,0:38:08.11,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会形成一个人造黑洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:08.20,0:38:10.91,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船就可以驶去太空任何地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:10.99,0:38:14.79,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑洞  宇宙最大的杀伤力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:15.20,0:38:17.75,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 而你制造出来 - 确实 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:17.83,0:38:22.92,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们运用那巨大的力量去扭曲时空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:23.00,0:38:26.59,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞧  洛斯克号要一千年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:26.67,0:38:28.93,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能驶到的星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:29.01,0:38:31.47,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地平线号朝发夕至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:31.55,0:38:34.72,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 行得通的话 - 下来吧 很安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:40.44,0:38:43.40,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么  贾斯汀如果被吸入通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:43.48,0:38:45.98,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会去了地平线号去过的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:46.07,0:38:48.53,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在理论上是的  但正如我说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:48.61,0:38:52.49,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 通道不可能自动打开 - 我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:52.58,0:38:54.28,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大副 封锁这间房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:54.37,0:38:56.24,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准任何人进出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:56.33,0:38:58.96,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 是 船长 - 船长  不用怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:59.04,0:39:01.08,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那通道 有三个磁场包藏着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:01.17,0:39:03.75,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 安全得很 - 安全?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:03.84,0:39:05.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的船受创
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:05.30,0:39:08.01,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一名船员垂危 威尔博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:08.09,0:39:10.59,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁也不准接近这东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:31.16,0:39:32.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:34.53,0:39:37.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日志上必定有些线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:38.54,0:39:40.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:44.13,0:39:45.34,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,DJ呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:05.52,0:40:09.03,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- DJ  你在哪里? - 在第四层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:02.83,0:41:04.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈咪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:16.89,0:41:18.14,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彼德丝!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:24.56,0:41:26.73,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事? 觉得怎样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:43.75,0:41:46.00,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你出去那么久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:46.08,0:41:47.83,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差点破我记录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:47.92,0:41:51.17,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听着  我宁可在外面呆上12个小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:51.25,0:41:53.63,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不愿在这鬼船上呆5秒钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:53.71,0:41:56.09,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,航行日志的最后记录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:56.59,0:41:59.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很以我的船员为荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:59.55,0:42:01.68,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,容我一提各船员的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:01.76,0:42:03.85,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基斯张波斯 珍妮丝吕宾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:04.56,0:42:07.02,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,班范达  迪克史密夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:09.23,0:42:10.65,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们已经抵达安全的距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:10.73,0:42:12.44,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是船长  乔伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:12.53,0:42:15.94,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在准备发动引力推进器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:16.07,0:42:18.95,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打开通往近纪时空区的通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:22.62,0:42:24.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等待我们的佳音 后会有期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:32.55,0:42:36.92,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 什么事?  - 我会试试弄清晰点儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:40.93,0:42:43.47,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 动力泄露 - 核心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:44.97,0:42:46.72,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别走开  陪着贾斯汀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:46.81,0:42:48.64,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得接近核心  博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:48.73,0:42:49.94,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:51.65,0:42:55.40,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 为什么泄露动力? - 磁场正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:55.48,0:42:58.74,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能线路烧了 我去检查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:58.82,0:43:00.41,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帮帮手 行吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:21.34,0:43:22.64,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:23.01,0:43:24.68,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀 你听见吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:25.64,0:43:27.81,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 他来了 - 谁来了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:29.85,0:43:31.64,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑暗 啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:48.66,0:43:50.87,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛病在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:04.18,0:44:15.25,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:15.26,0:44:17.44,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:31.25,0:44:33.74,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:45.39,0:44:46.64,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:47.60,0:44:49.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:49.56,0:44:51.77,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:56.94,0:44:58.44,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:59.44,0:45:00.73,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永远陪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:09.16,0:45:10.49,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威尔博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:37.31,0:45:40.23,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二氧化碳可以令人产生幻觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:40.32,0:45:42.40,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡说  DJ  那不是幻觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:42.48,0:45:43.86,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:44.03,0:45:46.32,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士 你在管道里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:46.53,0:45:48.95,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必定听到什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:50.16,0:45:52.83,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 必定见到什么 - 我见到 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:53.00,0:45:55.58,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1小时前 我见到我的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:55.66,0:45:58.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躺在手术桌上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:01.46,0:46:02.96,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 他的腿 ... - 彼得丝...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:03.05,0:46:04.88,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你不介意的话 我想说有点像休克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:06.30,0:46:08.13,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 你可能受惊过度 - 不 不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:08.22,0:46:10.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 会不会因为看见死尸?  - 对不起 不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:12.51,0:46:15.10,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死尸我见过 那是另一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:15.18,0:46:17.10,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她说得对  这是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:17.19,0:46:19.85,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明明感到热力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:19.98,0:46:22.86,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是幻觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:24.69,0:46:27.99,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿什 你有没有见到怪事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:28.53,0:46:31.07,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有  但不需要见到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:31.16,0:46:33.33,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:33.41,0:46:35.37,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这艘船邪门得很
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:35.50,0:46:38.12,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你的科学分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:38.21,0:46:40.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 别指望了 好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:40.38,0:46:41.33,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:41.42,0:46:42.63,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打破一切常理 不需要专家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:42.71,0:46:44.13,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁也知道要付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:44.21,0:46:47.47,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你害死一批  又想害死我们这一批
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:47.55,0:46:50.01,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 它只是一艘该死的船 - DJ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:50.09,0:46:53.18,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你走火入魔了 这艘船只是一堆金属
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:53.26,0:46:56.06,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 没有别的东西 - DJ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:00.06,0:47:02.19,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 没事 - DJ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:05.61,0:47:08.03,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 你没事吧?  - 没事 我只是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:08.74,0:47:10.07,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:10.24,0:47:11.78,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 见鬼 - 史密夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:11.91,0:47:13.99,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 没事了 - 操...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:14.08,0:47:17.58,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这趟他妈的死定 你给我冷静下来 立刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:19.41,0:47:22.17,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回楼上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:22.25,0:47:24.38,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和库珀出去  ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:24.46,0:47:26.88,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把船修妥 不准出错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:26.96,0:47:29.76,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出错 没人能回去了 明白吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:30.59,0:47:32.47,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 明白了 船长 - 那好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:33.14,0:47:34.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 船长 - 那就去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:41.98,0:47:43.69,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 米勒 - 什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:43.77,0:47:46.48,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我分析了生命探测的读数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:46.61,0:47:47.82,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,证明有生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:47.90,0:47:49.53,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但游离不定 这我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:49.61,0:47:52.36,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有没有中用的话可以说?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:52.45,0:47:55.24,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我有个理论 - 说来听听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:55.33,0:47:58.83,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为这些数据和幻觉有关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:58.91,0:48:02.58,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是一种防御本能的反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:02.67,0:48:04.25,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没空听这些话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:04.33,0:48:05.79,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 你必须得听 - 为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:05.88,0:48:09.38,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船对我们有反应而且越来越强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:09.46,0:48:13.01,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船似乎具有某种生命力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:13.09,0:48:15.72,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是指 这艘船是活的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:15.80,0:48:18.51,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要答案  我只有这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:18.60,0:48:22.10,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我要多活10个小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:06.98,0:49:08.23,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:09.57,0:49:15.70,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:06.92,0:50:09.13,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你听到吗? 你听到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:09.21,0:50:10.50,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 什么? - 你听到什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:10.59,0:50:12.00,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 你听到了 - 你听到什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:12.09,0:50:13.50,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 那是什么?  - 彼德丝  听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:13.59,0:50:14.88,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是DJ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:14.97,0:50:16.97,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们什么都没有听到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:17.05,0:50:18.34,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 冷静点 好吗 - 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:18.43,0:50:20.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 调整一下呼吸 - 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:20.55,0:50:22.64,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 现在 告诉我吧 - 我是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:27.06,0:50:29.81,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下来! 停下来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:31.23,0:50:32.77,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:34.23,0:50:35.74,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别这样!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:38.61,0:50:41.49,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 不! - 威尔博士 别走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:41.62,0:50:43.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想怎样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:46.46,0:50:50.62,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威尔博士 在目前情形下 自制很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:56.84,0:50:58.30,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:59.18,0:51:01.01,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前舱气锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:01.30,0:51:04.10,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒 史密夫 库珀 谁在气锁里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:04.18,0:51:05.97,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:06.64,0:51:07.85,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:10.65,0:51:12.31,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 贾斯汀 - 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:12.44,0:51:13.98,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:14.11,0:51:16.94,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀 不要! 贾斯汀 打开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:18.45,0:51:19.86,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒 来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:19.99,0:51:22.82,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒 情况危急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:22.95,0:51:24.78,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事? 斯塔克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:24.87,0:51:27.41,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 贾斯汀在气锁里 - 再说一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:27.50,0:51:30.37,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀在气锁里 没有穿气压衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:30.46,0:51:32.83,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 该死 我过去 - 你继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:32.96,0:51:35.46,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 别走开 我需要你帮忙 - 我必须去 你继续修理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:35.55,0:51:37.38,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他弄坏了内门开关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:37.51,0:51:39.51,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 你可以修复吗? - 我试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:40.01,0:51:41.26,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去救他 斯塔克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:41.34,0:51:44.22,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀 立刻开门!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:47.97,0:51:49.31,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斯塔克 报告情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:49.39,0:51:51.31,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:51.39,0:51:53.60,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我们打不开内门 - 我要装备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:53.69,0:51:56.48,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀 开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:00.86,0:52:04.03,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀 开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:04.16,0:52:06.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 你听到吗?  - 继续跟他谈话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:06.54,0:52:09.95,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到 你知道那是什么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:10.04,0:52:12.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它给东西你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:12.17,0:52:15.38,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 恐怖的东西 - 它是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:15.46,0:52:19.71,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是从别处闯进我心里面的黑暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:19.80,0:52:22.97,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我不要回去 - 不 熊宝宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:23.05,0:52:24.80,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 来吧 打开门 - 怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:24.89,0:52:27.14,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我还没修复好 - 它很不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:27.22,0:52:29.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没法说服他开门 不然他死定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:29.52,0:52:31.98,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 继续说服他 - 已经快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:32.06,0:52:34.44,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我快弄好了 - 贾斯汀和我们留在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:34.52,0:52:36.15,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快啊 快开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:36.23,0:52:39.65,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你见到我所见的就不会阻止我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:39.73,0:52:41.94,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你现在只是神志不清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:42.03,0:52:44.07,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 对了 就是那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:44.16,0:52:46.82,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开门 按那个键 快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:46.91,0:52:48.08,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的(外门  内门)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:50.08,0:52:51.08,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不(外门开动)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:53.42,0:52:56.92,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀按了键 外门30秒之后开启
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:57.00,0:52:59.09,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:02.72,0:53:06.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备25秒后减压
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:07.43,0:53:09.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:09.89,0:53:11.60,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 嘿 - 斯塔克 开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:11.68,0:53:12.93,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 嘿 开门 - 不能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:13.02,0:53:15.52,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外门一开 内门不能开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:15.60,0:53:17.69,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 否则整艘船会失压 - 天哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:17.77,0:53:20.61,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熊妈妈 开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:20.73,0:53:22.40,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快开门  求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:23.03,0:53:25.36,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 船长 - 让我跟他通话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:25.45,0:53:27.20,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船长 叫他们开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:27.28,0:53:29.12,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以 贾斯汀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:29.20,0:53:32.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我不想死在这里 - 你不会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:32.12,0:53:36.33,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心听着 我会救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:39.46,0:53:40.92,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:41.25,0:53:42.80,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经开始降压了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:43.22,0:53:45.72,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我的眼睛 - 别理会 闭上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:45.80,0:53:47.97,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽量紧闭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:48.09,0:53:49.18,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:49.26,0:53:52.56,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蹲下来  把身体卷成一团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:52.64,0:53:55.73,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能呼吸 老天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:55.98,0:53:58.23,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老天 好辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:58.31,0:54:02.57,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将肺里的气 尽量喷出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:02.65,0:54:05.65,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到吗? 喷尽肺里的气 贾斯汀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:07.32,0:54:08.99,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻喷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:21.00,0:54:22.67,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行了 熊宝宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:24.51,0:54:28.51,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我抓到他了 大家准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:28.59,0:54:29.93,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:31.97,0:54:35.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 有气压了 - 贾斯汀 我们来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:37.10,0:54:40.65,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腰部5处破裂 抱稳他的头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:41.44,0:54:42.65,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:44.69,0:54:47.03,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甘油 立刻拿来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:47.11,0:54:49.91,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,膈膜破裂 血压仍然下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:49.99,0:54:52.87,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始静脉滴注 15cc
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:01.29,0:55:04.80,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经止住了血 情况总算稳定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:06.21,0:55:09.13,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遍体鳞伤 但捡回条命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:09.47,0:55:12.05,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 假若可以回去... - 我们会回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:13.64,0:55:15.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斯塔克 我们还剩下多少时间?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:15.97,0:55:18.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空气只可以维持4个小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:19.64,0:55:20.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:20.98,0:55:23.73,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彼德丝 查查上一班船员出了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:23.82,0:55:26.48,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以免重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:26.57,0:55:30.82,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以在指挥室研究航行日志 但不会回医疗室去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:30.91,0:55:33.57,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 可以 - 我去查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:35.83,0:55:38.20,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀提过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:39.41,0:55:41.33,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"我心里面的黑暗"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:42.50,0:55:44.25,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:45.05,0:55:46.34,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:48.51,0:55:50.92,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为没有什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:55.26,0:55:57.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士 不要走开就算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:59.52,0:56:01.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要答案 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:01.44,0:56:04.02,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有个船员想走出船外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:04.11,0:56:08.28,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,企图自杀 我想知道那声音从何而来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:08.36,0:56:09.99,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船身遇到温度变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:10.07,0:56:14.99,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷缩热胀  产生震动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:15.08,0:56:19.12,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,废话! 你最清楚这艘船  却废话连篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:19.25,0:56:21.46,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要我说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:21.71,0:56:25.54,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说这船打开了一条通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:25.63,0:56:27.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 是的 - 通去哪里的通道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:28.76,0:56:30.51,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我不知道 - 它去过哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:30.59,0:56:33.55,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 这艘船去过哪里?  - 我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:33.64,0:56:36.05,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七年来 船去过哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:36.14,0:56:37.22,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:37.31,0:56:39.39,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"我不知道"不是一个好的回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:39.47,0:56:41.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你身为专家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:41.43,0:56:43.56,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有责任提供答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:43.65,0:56:47.48,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 所谓别处 即是哪处?  - 我不知道 我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:48.32,0:56:49.40,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:50.15,0:56:52.19,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这艘船有很多经历
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:52.28,0:56:55.74,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都不清楚 我需要时间去了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:57.12,0:56:58.33,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:58.91,0:57:02.16,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时间 我们刚好没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:07.34,0:57:08.67,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船长!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:14.93,0:57:24.60,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别把我留在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:30.02,0:57:31.32,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:34.61,0:57:38.49,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看在上帝的份上 救救我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:48.54,0:57:50.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的幻觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:52.88,0:57:54.88,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是幻觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:14.74,0:58:16.20,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上帝开恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:21.99,0:58:24.33,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真真切切的听见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:24.41,0:58:28.25,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人明明在呼唤我 一个叫做高利的年轻船员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:30.08,0:58:32.67,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他跟我一同在巨人号服役
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:34.01,0:58:38.18,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇上氧气缸爆裂  船内起火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:38.26,0:58:42.68,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和其他3人 逃上救生船 但高利赶不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:43.01,0:58:45.60,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,见到无重状态的火焰吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:47.52,0:58:49.10,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好灿烂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:51.27,0:58:53.02,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火焰水银泻地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:54.11,0:58:56.44,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四处流出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:57.61,0:58:59.36,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像波涛那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:00.91,0:59:03.41,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一浪接一浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:03.79,0:59:05.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不断向高利烧去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:07.71,0:59:10.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高利向我呼救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:11.29,0:59:12.96,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎样做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:13.46,0:59:15.80,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做唯一可以做的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:17.80,0:59:21.22,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我关上救生船的门 留下了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:25.27,0:59:27.81,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从此 我发誓不再放弃任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:29.10,0:59:31.27,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认识你很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:31.81,0:59:36.15,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 你从来没有提到过 - 这才奇怪 我从来没有向别人提起过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:37.57,0:59:39.82,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这艘船却知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:40.66,0:59:44.24,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看透我的恐惧 我的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:45.49,0:59:48.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进入我的脑海 向我展示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:49.75,0:59:52.17,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本来不打算告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:54.13,0:59:57.17,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反复听那求救讯号之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:57.34,0:59:58.84,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:00.93,1:00:03.93,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我发觉原来我翻译错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:12.69,1:00:13.94,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:15.19,1:00:17.52,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以为讯号是"释吾"
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:18.32,1:00:19.61,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:20.99,1:00:22.65,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不是"我"
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:23.78,1:00:26.20,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是"释汝"
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:27.29,1:00:28.83,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救你自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:29.70,1:00:31.46,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且越说越不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:35.17,1:00:36.38,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这段
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:37.67,1:00:39.05,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:39.84,1:00:42.97,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该是"脱冥"
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:44.47,1:00:46.14,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救你自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:48.56,1:00:49.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脱离地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:51.52,1:00:54.90,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞧 如果威尔博士没有说错
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:56.40,1:01:00.23,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这艘船一度走出我们的宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:00.36,1:01:02.57,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一度离开科学的境界
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:03.99,1:01:06.24,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天晓得它去到哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:06.70,1:01:08.41,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,见过什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:10.33,1:01:12.91,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带回来了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:13.25,1:01:14.62,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到过地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:18.84,1:01:22.09,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不相信有地狱吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:24.84,1:01:28.30,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发讯号的人必定相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:29.26,1:01:30.85,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:35.02,1:01:37.06,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,库珀 我希望是好消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:37.15,1:01:38.23,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:38.31,1:01:41.07,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-洛斯克号可以再加压
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:41.15,1:01:42.57,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,启航 我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:47.32,1:01:49.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小乖乖  别教我失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:57.25,1:02:00.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小乖乖  爹爹回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:00.84,1:02:02.38,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望接口支撑得住
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:03.63,1:02:04.84,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:04.92,1:02:07.84,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船长 船身仍有点漏气
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:07.93,1:02:10.01,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20分钟之内我可以填补好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:10.10,1:02:14.85,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,库珀先生 你是救星 20分钟后 我们启程
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:18.56,1:02:19.73,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒霉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:23.11,1:02:26.78,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 有没有咖啡? - 有 是冷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:26.86,1:02:28.11,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好极
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:38.46,1:02:39.67,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斯塔克
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:45.21,1:02:46.26,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:54.19,1:02:59.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,释汝  脱冥
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:07.24,1:03:08.53,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:11.57,1:03:13.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:14.83,1:03:16.54,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总署有命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:16.62,1:03:19.50,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命令是: 拯救船员 打捞机件
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:19.58,1:03:22.54,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船员都给你的船杀个精光 威尔博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:22.63,1:03:25.84,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我们有任务要执行 - 现在放弃任务 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:26.55,1:03:29.80,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斯塔克 下载地平线号的电脑档案
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:29.88,1:03:33.47,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,DJ 准备将贾斯汀搬上洛斯克号
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:33.55,1:03:36.01,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,医疗室有些东西我要去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:36.10,1:03:37.77,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题 去拿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:39.69,1:03:40.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 彼德丝 - 长官
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:40.98,1:03:43.10,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将二氧化碳清除器搬回洛斯克号
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:43.19,1:03:45.32,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 和史密夫一起 - 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:45.40,1:03:49.82,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:51.99,1:03:55.28,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 不要这样 - 已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:56.91,1:03:58.95,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的船呢?  怎可以不理?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:59.04,1:04:00.71,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会不理
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:00.79,1:04:02.79,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会将洛斯克号驶远一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:02.88,1:04:05.42,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后发飞弹 向地平线号猛轰
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:05.50,1:04:09.09,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它轰个稀巴烂  永不超生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:16.85,1:04:20.23,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船长 生命探测器读数在狂升
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:20.31,1:04:24.19,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核心似乎从船的其它部分吸收着动力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:24.27,1:04:27.15,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下载档案 撤离本船
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:27.23,1:04:30.69,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不可能撤离 它不准你走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:30.78,1:04:33.41,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,登上洛斯克号 否则你就要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:33.49,1:04:35.57,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走路回家 威尔博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:35.66,1:04:37.53,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:38.20,1:04:39.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:40.00,1:04:41.20,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:42.16,1:04:43.75,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:44.88,1:04:46.17,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:47.25,1:04:48.80,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 准备 - 没用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:54.05,1:04:55.68,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 没用了 - 好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:56.18,1:04:58.39,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧 这地方令人心寒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:58.47,1:05:00.10,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使回家也要呼吸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:00.18,1:05:02.39,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 够了 我们走 - 该死
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:02.94,1:05:04.31,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 25支 - 快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:04.40,1:05:06.40,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我们要25支 - 彼德丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:06.48,1:05:08.61,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 现在走人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:33.42,1:07:35.34,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,噢 不 彼德丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:41.43,1:07:43.05,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:48.98,1:07:50.02,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比利
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:00.15,1:08:01.40,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,琪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:08.91,1:08:09.95,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,琪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:11.62,1:08:13.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我 我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:15.80,1:08:17.34,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:21.26,1:08:24.26,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你需要我的时候我不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:25.30,1:08:27.18,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:27.89,1:08:31.06,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为工作 忽略了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:35.11,1:08:37.27,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,琪 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:38.11,1:08:41.78,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:41.86,1:08:43.86,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再一次  求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:44.66,1:08:53.58,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直都 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:55.42,1:08:57.42,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比利
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:58.09,1:08:59.75,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:02.59,1:09:06.30,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我多么寂寞 - 你不再寂寞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:07.76,1:09:11.47,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从此陪着我 跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:12.43,1:09:16.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有很多美妙的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:17.52,1:09:18.98,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:37.84,1:09:39.88,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是个高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:42.67,1:09:45.93,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,库珀 还有多久才修妥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:46.09,1:09:47.64,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好想起程
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:47.72,1:09:50.39,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不由你不佩服 修妥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:50.47,1:09:52.72,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收拾好工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:52.81,1:09:54.14,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就此走佬
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:54.23,1:09:56.39,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 顶多两分钟 - 知道
