Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:13.66,1:10:15.75,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威尔博士 立刻回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:15.83,1:10:17.46,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威尔博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:18.33,1:10:19.63,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,考
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:20.34,1:10:22.46,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒船长 米勒船长 听到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:22.84,1:10:25.26,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒船长 米勒船长 听到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:25.34,1:10:26.47,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说吧  史密夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:26.55,1:10:29.51,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威尔博士在洛斯克号内做了手脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:31.64,1:10:34.22,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等  我先检查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:39.81,1:10:42.23,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 史密夫 快走开 - 发生了什么事? 船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:42.32,1:10:44.23,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸弹失踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:44.32,1:10:46.74,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 威尔想炸毁洛斯克号 - 这怎么行?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:46.82,1:10:49.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 好不容易才修妥
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:49.53,1:10:51.87,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻离开洛斯克号 史密夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:01.00,1:11:03.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,操他娘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:25.53,1:11:27.19,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:27.28,1:11:29.24,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿什 等一等 我来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:43.21,1:11:44.25,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:51.55,1:11:53.97,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:36.81,1:12:38.18,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他奶奶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:38.27,1:12:41.27,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这么倒霉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:43.27,1:12:45.56,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,库珀 开动脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:46.02,1:12:49.73,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老子怎么回到船上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:49.82,1:12:53.36,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把气放了 把气放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:55.16,1:12:56.20,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他妈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:56.28,1:12:59.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你的气筒放气  这个方法最好行得通
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:59.87,1:13:03.66,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会回去的  一 二 三 去啊! 行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:03.96,1:13:07.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:08.63,1:13:11.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来也  狗杂种
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:18.01,1:13:19.18,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,DJ呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:20.39,1:13:22.52,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 发生什么事了? - 洛斯克号毁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:23.48,1:13:26.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 阿什 库珀殉职 - 什么....
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:26.48,1:13:29.48,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是威尔干的 碰到他 格杀勿论
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:29.82,1:13:31.23,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:31.82,1:13:34.82,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 小心  DJ - 放心好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:35.82,1:13:37.70,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会对付威尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:47.67,1:13:48.88,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,DJ在吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:01.18,1:14:04.77,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,DJ 回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:44.14,1:14:46.44,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船身修补
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:52.61,1:14:54.73,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 威尔博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:59.11,1:15:01.57,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你舍不得离开你的船?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:02.45,1:15:04.08,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你永远也不用离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:03.14,1:16:04.18,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斯塔克
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:26.66,1:16:28.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:32.21,1:16:34.33,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我扶你走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:37.34,1:16:38.55,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:42.88,1:16:44.22,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放松
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:59.74,1:17:01.78,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:03.57,1:17:05.53,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的眼睛咋了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:05.62,1:17:09.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要去的地方  用不着眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:09.54,1:17:11.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底在说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:11.54,1:17:15.46,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我制造地平线号 去探索星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:16.25,1:17:19.55,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但地平线号去得更远 更远
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:20.92,1:17:23.38,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我们的宇宙冲开了一个缺口
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:23.47,1:17:27.05,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一条通道 通往另一个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:27.72,1:17:30.10,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个彻底的乱世
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:30.93,1:17:33.39,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个彻底的凶域
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:33.89,1:17:37.36,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地平线号出发时  只是一艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:37.44,1:17:39.57,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但回来时
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:40.57,1:17:43.07,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是活生生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:44.28,1:17:46.11,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看它吧! 米勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:47.41,1:17:50.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多么壮丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:50.58,1:17:54.91,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这壮丽的船 杀光它的船员 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:55.79,1:17:57.25,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:58.79,1:18:01.13,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀光一批 有另一批
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:02.96,1:18:05.30,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在有我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:12.27,1:18:15.02,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在干什么? 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:15.10,1:18:18.27,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想知道船去过什么地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:18.77,1:18:20.98,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在你就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:34.79,1:18:39.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 你射不中我 就会射穿船身 - 你凭什么以为我射不中?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:40.88,1:18:42.50,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错  我回来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:42.63,1:18:45.38,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...该死 我不能…嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:45.47,1:18:47.47,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿 操
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:49.34,1:18:52.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什么鬼? 该死
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:27.36,1:20:30.40,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒 米勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:43.12,1:20:44.92,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伸手过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:53.93,1:20:56.26,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 快点 - 我不能够
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:58.10,1:20:59.93,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会撇下你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:19.95,1:21:21.62,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前舱气锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:27.09,1:21:28.59,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能是威尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:29.59,1:21:31.80,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不能大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:32.47,1:21:34.30,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许是他回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:45.15,1:21:47.27,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 不 不要打我 - 库珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:47.36,1:21:50.15,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帮我脱掉  帮我脱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:51.32,1:21:53.24,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 烤死我了 - 好了 好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:53.32,1:21:56.99,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 你没事了 麻烦总算过去 - 还没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:57.62,1:22:00.37,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引力推进器开动了 必须关闭
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:00.45,1:22:02.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 怎样关闭? 控制室已经被锁 - 机房呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:02.54,1:22:03.79,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以去机房关闭吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:03.87,1:22:06.37,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不懂程序 只有威尔博士是专家  但 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:06.46,1:22:08.42,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我宁死也不愿意去那个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:08.50,1:22:09.79,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:09.88,1:22:12.25,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我们就炸掉这杂种 - 炸掉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:12.34,1:22:15.51,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威尔说过 ...把主廊炸掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:16.30,1:22:20.26,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船头船尾一分为二 我们坐船头逃生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:20.76,1:22:22.93,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开动求救讯号
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:23.02,1:22:25.31,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后躺在引力缸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:25.39,1:22:27.14,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等候救援
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:27.23,1:22:29.61,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我立刻去启动爆炸装置
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:29.69,1:22:31.90,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 行得通吗?  - 威尔说过行得通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:31.98,1:22:34.28,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你开动求救讯号之后  立刻回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:34.36,1:22:36.15,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 遵命 - 我跟你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:36.24,1:22:38.32,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你留在这里  准备引力缸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:38.41,1:22:39.49,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:41.70,1:22:44.04,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出去之后 你关上门
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:53.84,1:22:57.88,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通道5分钟之后打开 人手引爆准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:04.27,1:23:06.68,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求救讯号开动
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:08.56,1:23:10.40,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:10.56,1:23:11.90,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,血?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:19.24,1:23:21.07,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邪门
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:21.74,1:23:23.24,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该死
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:24.20,1:23:49.89,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斯塔克
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:54.27,1:23:55.65,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:58.32,1:24:02.74,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通道3分钟之后打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:06.62,1:24:09.79,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随时可以引爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:10.58,1:24:13.46,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爆炸装置已启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:13.63,1:24:15.75,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,装置启动 可以引爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:16.09,1:24:19.09,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重复 装置启动 可以引爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:19.51,1:24:21.93,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒 米勒 你听到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:22.01,1:24:24.09,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要立刻走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:26.64,1:24:28.35,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你见死不救
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:45.99,1:24:50.66,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通道1分钟之后打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:06.97,1:25:08.01,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:27.70,1:25:29.66,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不顾而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:32.04,1:25:35.08,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是高利 高利已经死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:39.50,1:25:41.00,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威尔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:43.55,1:25:47.47,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这艘船叫我来 不会放我走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:47.55,1:25:49.76,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会放走任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:49.89,1:25:52.68,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真以为可以毁掉这船?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:53.02,1:25:56.06,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这艘船穿越时空
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:56.60,1:26:00.11,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去过你无法想象的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:00.23,1:26:01.94,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:02.40,1:26:06.66,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 是时候回去了 - 回去地狱 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:06.74,1:26:10.12,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你什么也不知道 地狱只是个名称
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:10.58,1:26:14.91,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实际情形比地狱悲惨得多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:17.58,1:26:20.59,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我给你看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:21.96,1:26:23.26,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帮我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:26.59,1:26:28.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:30.47,1:26:32.18,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:32.27,1:26:34.02,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 看到没有? - 不
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:34.10,1:26:37.81,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们没有死去 暂时没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:37.94,1:26:39.31,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:41.11,1:26:46.24,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你害我的船员
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:06.01,1:27:09.84,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们已经是这艘船的附属品了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:09.97,1:27:11.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通道打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:26.49,1:27:27.82,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:28.66,1:27:30.53,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带我走 放过他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:30.62,1:27:34.16,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 大局已定
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:36.29,1:27:38.12,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通道打开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:38.21,1:27:41.17,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们通通跟我走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:45.84,1:27:57.18,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看见没有?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:59.85,1:28:01.19,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:02.56,1:28:04.36,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:07.69,1:28:09.40,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:30.19,1:29:31.23,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:33.85,1:29:35.57,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,72日后
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:38.70,1:29:41.62,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是拯救一号 找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:43.25,1:29:46.63,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在驶近地平线号的残骸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:46.71,1:29:48.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备登船
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:57.89,1:30:00.26,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在进入引力区
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:00.93,1:30:04.94,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎抵受得起爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:06.48,1:30:08.65,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生还者有三名
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:09.11,1:30:12.40,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,库珀 贾斯汀 斯塔克
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:13.15,1:30:16.07,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贾斯汀受了重伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:16.16,1:30:17.91,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但仍然活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:19.83,1:30:22.33,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引力缸仍然有动力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:24.91,1:30:27.17,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在打开第一引力缸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:37.30,1:30:39.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要怕 没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:39.51,1:30:41.43,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 脱险了 - 贾斯汀 库珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:41.51,1:30:43.85,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们都脱险了 跟我们一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:45.35,1:30:47.02,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟我们一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:49.69,1:30:52.94,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 斯塔克 斯塔克 - 冷静点 没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:53.03,1:30:54.94,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 冷静点  是我 - 深呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:55.03,1:30:56.24,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 斯塔克 - 深呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:56.32,1:30:58.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我们是救援队 - 快拿镇定剂来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:58.53,1:31:01.45,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我了解 斯塔克 我了解 - 没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:01.83,1:31:03.29,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快拿镇定剂来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:03.37,1:31:05.37,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斯塔克 是救援队 我们脱险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:05.46,1:31:08.21,ChText,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 好了 好了 快拿来 - 我们脱险了

